ObjectStates.Name: Notecard
ObjectStates.Description:
First commando starting from Team leader and going clockwise is the [i]commanding officer[/i].
Commanding officer determines commandos' player order each round by assigning priority cards.
1. Team Leader
2. Countermeasures Specialist
3. Heavy Support Specialist
4. Rifleman
5. Reconnaissance Specialist
